description:
This BOA-B (Black-Ops Amphibious Breacher) fixed blade from Medford Knife and Tool was designed for Naval Special Warfare operators. This is a purpose-driven knife design that utilizes a strong 1/4 inch thick D2 steel build. The dagger blade is double-edged and partially serrated along the top edge. The full-tang blade has integrated guards and a pry tip. Skeletonized flamed titanium scales with built-in wrenches and gripper. The BOA-B comes with a Kydex sheath with TekLok. Knife is in excellent condition, shows no signs of use or carry. <br>
